# zaturarc

## settings
set window-height 1120
set window-width 768
set adjust-open width
#set synctex-editor-command synctex

## common
map [all]  <C-g> abort



## normal
### move
map [normal] k scroll down
map [normal] i scroll up
map [normal] l scroll right
map [normal] j scroll left
map [normal] <C-k> scroll down
map [normal] <C-i> scroll up
map [normal] <C-l> scroll right
map [normal] <C-j> scroll left

map [normal] u goto top
map [normal] o goto bottom
map [normal] <C-u> goto top
map [normal] <C-o> goto bottom

map [normal] , navigate previous
map [normal] . navigate next
map [normal] <C-,> navigate previous
map [normal] <C-.> navigate next

map [normal] @ mark_add
map [normal] ^ mark_evaluate
map [normal] <C-@> mark_add
map [normal] <C-^> mark_evaluate

map [normal] <Button9> navigate previous
map [normal] <Button8> navigate next

### zoom
map [normal] <+> zoom in
map [normal] <;> zoom in
map [normal] <-> zoom out
map [normal] <C-;> zoom in
map [normal] <C--> zoom out


### search
map [normal] s feedkeys /
map [normal] r feedkeys ?
map [normal] <C-s> search forward
map [normal] <C-r> search backward

## fullscreen
map [fullscreen] k scroll down
map [fullscreen] i scroll up
map [fullscreen] l scroll right
map [fullscreen] j scroll left
map [fullscreen] <C-k> scroll down
map [fullscreen] <C-i> scroll up
map [fullscreen] <C-l> scroll right
map [fullscreen] <C-j> scroll left

map [fullscreen] u goto top
map [fullscreen] o goto bottom
map [fullscreen] <C-u> goto top
map [fullscreen] <C-o> goto bottom

map [fullscreen] , navigate previous
map [fullscreen] . navigate next
map [fullscreen] <C-,> navigate previous
map [fullscreen] <C-.> navigate next

map [fullscreen] @ mark_add
map [fullscreen] ^ mark_evaluate
map [fullscreen] <C-@> mark_add
map [fullscreen] <C-^> mark_evaluate

map [fullscreen] <Button9> navigate previous
map [fullscreen] <Button8> navigate next

### zoom
map [fullscreen] <+> zoom in
map [fullscreen] <;> zoom in
map [fullscreen] <-> zoom out
map [fullscreen] <C-;> zoom in
map [fullscreen] <C--> zoom out


### search
map [fullscreen] s feedkeys /
map [fullscreen] r feedkeys ?
map [fullscreen] <C-s> search forward
map [fullscreen] <C-r> search backward

## index
### move 
map [index] k navigate_index down
map [index] i navigate_index up
map [index] j navigate_index collapse
map [index] l navigate_index expand
map [index] <C-k> navigate_index down
map [index] <C-i> navigate_index up
map [index] <C-j> navigate_index collapse
map [index] <C-l> navigate_index expand


