## insert

## toggle
### normal <-> fullscreen
map [normal] f toggle_fullscreen
map [fullscreen] f toggle_fullscreen
map [normal] <C-f> toggle_fullscreen
map [fullscreen] <C-f> toggle_fullscreen

### normal <-> index
map [normal] <Tab> toggle_index
map [index] <Tab> toggle_index

### normal <-> inputbar
map [normal] x feedkeys :
#map [inputbar] x toggle_inputbar

### normal <-> page_mode
map [all] p toggle_page_mode 2
map  t set pages-per-row 1

